\page page_idoc idoc - Document Framework

\section intro_sec Introduction

The idoc library provides a template-based document management framework with support for
multi-level undo/redo, document persistence, and document-view architecture.

\section features_sec Key Features

- **Document Templates**: Template-based document creation
- **Multi-Document Management**: Managing multiple documents simultaneously
- **Undo/Redo**: Multi-level undo mechanism based on serialization
- **Document Persistence**: File-based document storage and loading
- **Model-Observer**: Document change notification and observation
- **Composite Documents**: Complex documents composed of multiple templates

\section architecture_sec Architecture

Key components:

- **idoc::IDocument**: Base document interface
- **idoc::IDocumentTemplate**: Document template interface
- **idoc::CMultiDocumentManagerBase**: Multi-document manager base class
- **idoc::CCompositeDocumentTemplateComp**: Composite document template
- **idoc::CMultiLevelUndoComp**: Multi-level undo/redo implementation

\section dependencies Dependencies

- **istd**: Standard utilities and interfaces
- **iser**: Serialization framework
- **icomp**: Component framework
- **imod**: Model-observer pattern

\section see_also See Also

- idoc::IDocument
- idoc::IDocumentTemplate
- idoc::CMultiDocumentManagerBase

*/
